            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nIn this text, we will deepen our knowledge of decimal systems, including our own and the Andean decimal system. We recommend studying the following texts before continuing:\n\n- **Numerical Families (Part I)**: Examines the relationship between numbers and our families (<htcite0>).\n- **Numerical Families (Part II)**: Studies the relationship between families and numerical orders (<htcite1>).\n- **Chapter 4**: Dedicated to studying multiplication tables (<htcite2>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "00f3ab60-2017-420a-99dc-56de384243e8",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "Numerical Families (Part I)",
